00:36:34,947 --> 00:36:36,655
[SNICKERS]

503
00:36:43,362 --> 00:36:45,612
[SIGHS]

504
00:36:45,612 --> 00:36:47,071
Mm-hm.

505
00:36:47,071 --> 00:36:49,195
Lighter, check.

506
00:36:49,195 --> 00:36:51,278
Bong, check.

507
00:36:51,278 --> 00:36:52,778
[LAUGHS]

508
00:36:52,778 --> 00:36:54,236
Ignite.

509
00:37:11,775 --> 00:37:14,233
[CHUCKLES]

510
00:37:14,233 --> 00:37:16,649
♪ I'll be there ♪

