00:37:16,649 --> 00:37:18,316
[SNICKERING]

512
00:37:18,316 --> 00:37:20,024
[BUBBLES]

513
00:37:23,981 --> 00:37:24,898
[GROWLING]

514
00:37:24,898 --> 00:37:26,690
Oh, shit--

515
00:37:27,565 --> 00:37:28,815
Sh--

516
00:37:28,815 --> 00:37:30,397
[COUGHING]

517
00:37:30,397 --> 00:37:31,522
Oh...

518
00:37:31,522 --> 00:37:32,814
[COUGHS]

519
00:37:34,897 --> 00:37:36,146
Shit.

520
00:37:37,021 --> 00:37:38,271
Shit!

521
00:37:41,021 --> 00:37:42,812
Oh, shit.

