[SCOFFS]
You're so full of shit.

1298
01:27:51,828 --> 01:27:54,285
I'm serious.

1299
01:27:54,285 --> 01:27:56,994
It all happened
in our building.

1300
01:27:56,994 --> 01:27:58,952
Seriously?

1301
01:27:58,952 --> 01:28:00,909
They just changed the name

1302
01:28:00,909 --> 01:28:04,284
so no one would be scared
to live here.

1303
01:28:04,284 --> 01:28:07,908
After all, who wants
to live in a building

1304
01:28:07,908 --> 01:28:11,950
where they found bodies
in the heating vents?

1305
01:28:11,950 --> 01:28:12,741
[GIGGLES]

1306
01:28:23,615 --> 01:28:26,156
What's wrong,
are you scared?

1307
01:28:26,156 --> 01:28:27,989
I'm annoyed.

1308
01:28:30,280 --> 01:28:33,196
I'm going to the library.

1309
01:28:33,196 --> 01:28:35,613
Where it's quiet.

1310
01:28:35,613 --> 01:28:36,779
Come on,

1311
01:28:36,779 --> 01:28:39,404
I was just kidding around.
I'll be quiet.

1312
01:28:41,195 --> 01:28:43,445
I will see you
in the morning.

1313
01:28:43,445 --> 01:28:46,653
Seriously, I'll be quiet.

1314
01:28:49,111 --> 01:28:51,861
You don't wanna be in here
alone, do you?

1315
01:28:51,861 --> 01:28:53,610
Don't be ridiculous.

1316
01:28:53,610 --> 01:28:55,068
[CHUCKLES]

1317
01:28:57,943 --> 01:28:59,693
[JENNIFER CHUCKLES]

1318
01:28:59,693 --> 01:29:01,859
Hey, Amy.

1319
01:29:01,859 --> 01:29:04,067
Don't let the Boogeyman
get you.

1320
01:29:05,275 --> 01:29:06,192
[GAGS]

1321
01:29:11,358 --> 01:29:12,941
Whatever.

1322
01:29:19,523 --> 01:29:22,356
[♪]

1323
01:29:26,272 --> 01:29:27,521
[DOOR CREAKS OPEN]

1324
01:29:32,105 --> 01:29:34,562
Changed your mind, huh?

1325
01:29:34,562 --> 01:29:37,770
Too scared to walk
to the library alone?

1326
01:30:08,016 --> 01:30:09,849
[BED CREAKS]

1327
01:30:13,140 --> 01:30:14,140
Oh, ha-ha.

1328
01:30:14,140 --> 01:30:17,848
Jennifer,
you're hilarious.

1329
01:30:17,848 --> 01:30:19,931
Wait.

1330
01:30:19,931 --> 01:30:22,430
It's not Jennifer.

1331
01:30:22,430 --> 01:30:24,513
Who could it be?

1332
01:30:24,513 --> 01:30:25,722
[GASPS]

1333
01:30:25,722 --> 01:30:27,097
No.

1334
01:30:27,097 --> 01:30:29,846
Is it the Boogeyman?

1335
01:30:29,846 --> 01:30:31,304
[CHUCKLES]

1336
01:30:34,971 --> 01:30:38,220
All right, I admit it.
I was scared, okay?

1337
01:30:43,094 --> 01:30:44,844
[CREAKS]

1338
01:30:46,927 --> 01:30:48,510
[GROWLING]

1339
01:30:48,510 --> 01:30:50,509
[SCREAMING]

1340
01:30:59,175 --> 01:31:02,092
[♪]